Comment_contributor: Used not in sequence to the four numbers above, but to indicate a separate substantive quantity. [cf. p.107 <tond> ‘arm’; p.122 <tonda> ‘hand’]
Comment_glosser: Related to ‘arm’ (?); said by the contributor to not be used in a counting series as are ‘one’ through ‘four’
Numerals higher than 5 are questionable, since “5” itself is said not to behave like a cardinal numeral
